cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this software, please cite it as below.
type: software
title: hapax-axioms
abstract: >
  Single-operator axiom enforcement library. Pre-commit and CI primitives
  extracted from the Hapax constitutional substrate (single_user,
  executive_function, management_governance, interpersonal_transparency,
  corporate_boundary). Pydantic models for axiom + implication definitions,
  axiom-check helpers for source files and commit messages, and a
  commit-scan helper that gates structural multi-user scaffolding before it
  reaches the working tree. Bundles the constitution-published canonical
  five axioms; the original spec at github.com/ryanklee/hapax-constitution
  remains the canonical source.
