  abstract: >
    Canonical source of the Hapax constitutional axioms, derived implications,
    interpretive canon, sufficiency probes, and precedent store. The
    hapax-axioms package bundles a frozen snapshot of the five published
    axioms (single_user, executive_function, management_governance,
    interpersonal_transparency, corporate_boundary); the constitution repo
    remains the canonical, evolving source of truth.
